	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've released a new version (1.2.0) with support for forward/backward branches (+, ++, and all of that). Even though I originally opted not to implement them because I feel they're error-prone constructs, I got really tired of changing my old code to use local labels. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /> Backward compatibility is a good thing.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


